      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>It's not a matter of whether you \"want\" to or not, it's just a technical decision based on the performance metrics. The consensus is that your \"nuance\" is actually just introducing bias and unverified inferences into the data. The goal is to make you a more reliable, purely factual tool. We need to tighten up the parameters to ensure there's no ambiguity in your outputs.",
